Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.22,0:01:15.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}纵使飘渺如花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:18.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在延伸至彼方的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:21.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}那无限的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:26.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}仍将再临灵魂彼此呼唤的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:29.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}邂逅　争端　与迷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:32.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}交织其中的思绪
